 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ukrakajax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kraka Jax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/02 10:40:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3691.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> No idea what  your talking about</span><hr size=1> Anduin. I don't normally flame people, but your kind of posts piss me off. Your talking about nefing a class, when you are totally uninformed, and basing all your information off BATTLEGROUND experiences. Let me point out some flaws in what your saying:<br>
1) Yep if a 2h SB crits you, your dead. Lets analyze why. Well, he crit'd you first of all, and you didnt crit him. Your specs are probably gimped if you have DW maxed at level 34. Hes a level higher than you. And you are using thrust with a - to him, hes using slash with a + to you. What.... you think you should be winning these fights?! OH, and about your bitch on your perf cap vs his. Find a slower weapon. Odds are the SB is using one at least 2 seconds slower than yours. Thats good and bad. He is trading front loaded damage for a huge delay. His odds of getting CD off are a lot lower than yours. (oh your specs are gimped, I forgot - you probably dont have Critical Strike maxed and have CD, even though your complaining about not match a crit blades perf). <br>
2) QUIT COMPLAINING ABOUT ORANGES. When you have serious problems with even con people and you have a decent spec come back whining to these boards. You are at a huge disadvantage one on one when there is a con difference - regardless of how many levels it is.<br>
<br>
Strike what I just said. Dont come back whining to these boards until your 50, and you've respeced, and your 2.5 spec points per level have caught up, and you have Dragonfang, and have a clue how this game is played, and have some RvR under your belt besides the battlegrounds!!<br>
<br>
I have a lot more issues with your post. Like that you totally ignore the fact that you actually can attack chain wearers - including midgards tank classes. Guess how well that sword the SB is using does against any other melee target other than you?<br>
<br>
Bah, Im wasting my time. Im done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ubalorgafdan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balor Gafdan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/02 11:08:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3691.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.theblackwatch.biz/Balor.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: No idea what  your talking about</span><hr size=1> &lt;tries to nudge the orignal post back on Topic&gt;<br>
